USE CASE: 11 access the number of people who speak the following the following languages from greatest number to smallest, including the percentage of the world population: Chinese, English, Hindi, Spanish, Arabic.

CHARACTERISTIC INFORMATION
Goal in Context

As the organisation, I would like to access the number of people who speak the following the following languages from greatest number to smallest, including the percentage of the world population: Chinese, English, Hindi, Spanish, Arabic.
Scope
Company.

Level
Primary task.

Preconditions
Database contains the population that speaks Chinese, English, Hindi, Spanish, Arabic, and the total world population.

Success End Condition
A report is available for the organisation to analyse.

Failed End Condition
No report is produced.

Primary Actor
Organisation

Trigger
A request for the data is made


EXTENSIONS
None.
SUB-VARIATIONS
None.

SCHEDULE
